text: Joo Yea-na (born 5 February 1990) is a South Korean female professional volleyball player. She was part of the team at the Asian Women's U19 Volleyball Championship, and 2011 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup. ==Clubs== *Heungkuk life Insurance (2011) ==References== ==External links== * Player info FIVB Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean women's volleyball players
